00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:51,000
 If, open parenthesis, index, open parenthesis, line, double quote, the, double quote, close parenthesis, greater than or equal to 0, close parenthesis, printf, open parenthesis, double quote, percent s, double quote, line, close parenthesis, semicolon, and close curly brace to finish the main function.

